<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>التحقق الثنائي | بوابة التنفيذ</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.rtl.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #0f3460 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .verify-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .icon-box {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.1);
            color: #e94560;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }
        .otp-input {
            letter-spacing: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .otp-input:focus {
            border-color: #e94560;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.25);
        }
        .btn-verify {
            background: #e94560;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-verify:hover {
            background: #d8315b;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="verify-card">
        <div class="icon-box">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
        </div>
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-2">التحقق بخطوتين</h4>
        <p class="text-muted small mb-4">تم إرسال كود من 6 أرقام إلى حسابك في تيليجرام (في البوت المخصص لك). يرجى إدخاله هنا.</p>

        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-danger fw-bold small rounded-3 mb-4">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-exclamation me-1"></i> <%= error %>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <form action="/executor-portal/verify" method="POST">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <input type="text" name="otp" class="form-control otp-input bg-light" placeholder="------" maxlength="6" autocomplete="off" required dir="ltr">
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-verify w-100 text-white shadow mb-3">تأكيد الرمز <i class="fa-solid fa-check ms-1"></i></button>
            
            <a href="/login" class="text-muted small text-decoration-none hover-danger"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right me-1"></i> العودة لتسجيل الدخول</a>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>